MODULES MEAN NOT REPEATING EVERY WHERE
EX - A ="SRIKANTH" THEN {SRIKANTH} WONT REPEAT EVERYWHERE WE CAN USE A
    EX - VARIABLE
    FUNCTIONS
    ANSIBLE ROLES
    LOCALS

*MODULES =ITS LIKE A FUNCTION YOU CAN USE AS A KEY TOGET INFRA X = SRIKANTH*

